                            <description>
                                <langstring>Resource Bank ID: ELO1238430 -  In this activity, students will refresh their understanding of chemistry and study simple organic molecules.  Students will build upon their understanding of chemistry and study large complex molecules that make up living things such as proteins, carbohydrates, lipids and nucleic acids.  Finally, students will apply their knowledge by putting large molecules together in chemical reactions and completing a food testing lab for the presence of macromolecules studied so far.</langstring>
